t-white\" style=\"font-size:14px\">Know More</span><span class=\"\n          w-0\n          opacity-0\n          overflow-hidden\n          transition-all\n          duration-300\n          ease-in-out\n          flex\n          items-center\n          ml-0\n          group-hover:w-6 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:ml-3\n        \"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 text-[var(--text-light)]\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 28 26\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"transform scale-x-[-1] \"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M0.73645 11.9334L0.762199 11.9356V11.9313H0.868309C6.38999 11.4816 10.7393 6.64917 10.7393 0.752352L10.7363 0.5H12.7616L12.7646 0.752352C12.7646 5.43486 10.4581 9.55228 6.971 11.9313L27.2646 11.9356V14.0622L6.95452 14.0579C10.4519 16.4348 12.7646 20.5576 12.7646 25.2476L12.7616 25.5H10.7363L10.7393 25.2476C10.7393 19.3239 6.35084 14.4742 0.792076 14.0622L0.735416 14.0666V14.0579V11.9431V11.9345L0.73645 11.9334Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></svg></div></span></button></div></div></div><div class=\"text-center leading-[1.2] flex flex-col gap-[32px] items-center\"><div class=\"w-[90%] flex flex-col gap-[28px]\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 pb-4\"><span class=\"text-base font-bold text-[var(--color-primary)]\" style=\"font-size:30px\">Luxury You Can Feel</span> <span class=\"inline-block text-center leading-snug leading-[1.2]\"><span class=\"text-base font-medium text-[var(--link-color)] leading-[1.2]\" style=\"font-size:14px\"> From soundproof walls to premium finishes, our builds are engineered for perfection. </span><span class=\"text-base font-medium text-[var(--link-color)] leading-[1.2]\" style=\"font-size:14px\"> We don’t just build modular; we build to a higher standard. Quality isn’t a goal—it’s our foundation.</span></span></div><div class=\"flex flex-row w-full gap-4 justify-center\"><button class=\"\n        group\n        cursor-pointer\n        border \n        rounded-full\n        py-[8px] \n        px-[16px]\n        md:py-[16px] \n        md:px-[28px] // Changed from 36px to 28px\n        flex \n        items-center \n        justify-center\n        transition-all\n        duration-300\n        border-[var(--color-primary)] bg-[var(--text-light)] hover:bg-[var(--color-primary)]\n        \n      \"><span class=\"text-base font-bold text-[var(--color-primary)] transition-colors duration-300 group-hover:text-white\" style=\"font-size:14px\">Schedule a Visit</span><span class=\"\n          w-0\n          opacity-0\n          overflow-hidden\n          transition-all\n          duration-300\n          ease-in-out\n          flex\n          items-center\n          ml-0\n          group-hover:w-6 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:ml-3\n        \"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 text-[var(--text-light)]\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 28 26\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"transform scale-x-[-1] \"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M0.73645 11.9334L0.762199 11.9356V11.9313H0.868309C6.38999 11.4816 10.7393 6.64917 10.7393 0.752352L10.7363 0.5H12.7616L12.7646 0.752352C12.7646 5.43486 10.4581 9.55228 6.971 11.9313L27.2646 11.9356V14.0622L6.95452 14.0579C10.4519 16.4348 12.7646 20.5576 12.7646 25.2476L12.7616 25.5H10.7363L10.7393 25.2476C10.7393 19.3239 6.35084 14.4742 0.792076 14.0622L0.735416 14.0666V14.0579V11.9431V11.9345L0.73645 11.9334Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></svg></div></span></button></div></div><div class=\"w-full aspect-[4/3] relative\"><img alt=\"cabin-section\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:contain;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image/?url=%2Fassets%2Fcabin%2Fcabin_1.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image/?url=%2Fassets%2Fcabin%2Fcabin_1.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image/?url=%2Fassets%2Fcabin%2Fcabin_1.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image/?url=%2Fassets%2Fcabin%2Fcabin_1.png&amp