t-base font-bold text-[var(--color-primary)] leading-[1.2]\" style=\"font-size:30px\">Saharsh </span><span class=\"text-base font-bold text-[var(--text-dark)] leading-[1.2]\" style=\"font-size:30px\">Advantage</span></span><span class=\"text-base font-normal text-[var(--text-dark)]\" style=\"font-size:14px\">Why wait months when you can be ready in weeks?<!-- --> </span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center gap-3 text-center max-md:hidden\"><span class=\"inline-block text-center leading-snug \"><span class=\"text-base font-bold text-[var(--text-dark)] leading-[1.2]\" style=\"font-size:clamp(60px, 5.208vw, 75px)\">The </span><span class=\"text-base font-bold text-[var(--color-primary)] leading-[1.2]\" style=\"font-size:clamp(60px, 5.208vw, 75px)\">Saharsh </span><span class=\"text-base font-bold text-[var(--text-dark)] leading-[1.2]\" style=\"font-size:clamp(60px, 5.208vw, 75px)\">Advantage</span></span><span class=\"text-base font-normal text-[var(--text-dark)]\" style=\"font-size:clamp(16px, 1.389vw, 20px)\">Why wait months when you can be ready in weeks?<!-- --> </span></div><div style=\"width:100%;max-width:1000px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));gap:16px;align-items:start\"><div style=\"border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;background:var(--color-primary)\"><div style=\"padding:24px 24px 0\" class=\"flex flex-col\"><span class=\"w-fit\" style=\"display:inline-block;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:999px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);color:#fff;margin-bottom:12px\">✦ Recommended</span><span class=\"text-base font-bold text-[var(--text-light)]\" style=\"font-size:clamp(26px, 2.222vw, 32px)\">Saharsh Cabins</span><span class=\"text-base font-normal text-[var(--text-light)]\" style=\"font-size:clamp(13px, 1.111vw, 16px)\">Stop wasting time. Start building smarter.<!-- --> </span></div><div style=\"height:0.5px;margin:16px 24px 0;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.25)\"></div><ul style=\"padding:0 24px 24px;margin:0;list-style:none\"><li class=\"items-center\" style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:12px 0;min-height:48px;border-bottom:0.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15)\"><svg style=\"flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"9\" r=\"9\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\"></circle><path d=\"M5 9.5L7.5 12L13 6.5\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-base font-normal text-[var(--text-light)]\" style=\"font-size:14px\">Get operational 30–60% faster — no waiting, no delays\t</span></li><li class=\"items-center\" style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:12px 0;min-height:48px;border-bottom:0.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15)\"><svg style=\"flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"9\" r=\"9\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\"></circle><path d=\"M5 9.5L7.5 12L13 6.5\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-base font-normal text-[var(--text-light)]\" style=\"font-size:14px\">Lock your budget upfront — no hidden costs, ever</span></li><li class=\"items-center\" style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:12px 0;min-height:48px;border-bottom:0.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15)\"><svg style=\"flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"9\" r=\"9\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\"></circle><path d=\"M5 9.5L7.5 12L13 6.5\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-base font-normal text-[var(--text-light)]\" style=\"font-size:14px\">Factory-built precision — zero compromise on quality\t</span></li><li class=\"items-center\" style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:12px 0;min-height:48px;border-bottom:0.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15)\"><svg style=\"flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"9\" r=\"9\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\"></circle><path d=\"M5 9.5L7.5 12L13 6.5\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-base font-normal text-[var(--text-light)]\" style=\"font-size:14px\">Install in weeks, not months — minimal site chaos\t</span></li><li class=\"items-center\" style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:12px 0;min-height:48px;border-bottom:0.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15)\"><svg style=\"flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"9\" r=\"9\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\"></circle><path d=\"M5 9.5L7.5 12L13 6.5\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-base font-normal text-[var(--text-light)]\" style=\"font-size:14px\">Cut waste by up to 90% — smarter, cleaner construction\t</span></li><li class=\"items-center\" style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:12px 0;min-height:48px;border-bottom:0.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15)\"><svg style=\"flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"9\" r=\"9\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\"></circle><path d=\"M5 9.5L7.5 12L13 6.5\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-base font-normal text-[var(--text-light)]\" style=\"font-size:14px\">Built for Site conditions — durable, reliable, proven\t</span></li><li class=\"items-center\" style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:12px 0;min-height:48px;border-bottom:0.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15)\"><svg style=\"flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"9\" r=\"9\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\"></circle><path d=\"M5 9.5L7.5 12L13 6.5\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-base font-normal text-[var(--text-light)]\" style=\"font-size:14px\">Scale instantly when you grow — no rework, no hassle\t</span></li><li class=\"items-center\" style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:12px 0;min-height:48px;border-bottom:none\"><svg style=\"flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"9\" r=\"9\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.2)\"></circle><path d=\"M5 9.5L7.5 12L13 6.5\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-base font-normal text-[var(--text-light)]\" style=\"font-size:14px\">Premium finish, every single time — consistency you can trust\t</span></li></ul></div><div style=\"border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;background:#fff;border:0.5px solid var(--color-border, #e5e7eb)\"><div style=\"padding:24px 24px 0\" class=\"flex flex-col\"><span class=\"w-fit\" style=\"display:inline-block;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:999px;background:#f3f4f6;color:#6b7280;margin-bottom:12px\">Traditional</span><span class=\"text-base font-bold text-[var(--text-dark)]\" style=\"font-size:clamp(26px, 2.222vw, 32px)\">Traditional Construction</span><span class=\"text-base font-normal text-[var(--text-muted)]\" style=\"font-size:clamp(13px, 1.111vw, 16px)\">Slow. Unpredictable. Expensive.<!-- --> </span></div><div style=\"height:0.5px;margin:16px 24px 0;background:#e5e7eb\"></div><ul style=\"padding:0 24px 24px;margin:0;list-style:none\"><li class=\"items-center\" style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:12px 0;min-height:48px;border-bottom:0.5px solid #e5e7eb\"><svg style=\"flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"9\" r=\"9\" fill=\"rgba(239,68,68,0.1)\"></circle><path d=\"M6 6l6 6M12 6l-6 6\" stroke=\"#ef4444\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-base font-normal text-[var(--text-dark)]\" style=\"font-size:14px\">Stuck for 12–24+ months before you even start operating\t</span></li><li class=\"items-center\" style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:12px 0;min-height:48px;border-bottom:0.5px solid #e5e7eb\"><svg style=\"flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"9\" r=\"9\" fill=\"rgba(239,68,68,0.1)\"></circle><path d=\"M6 6l6 6M12 6l-6 6\" stroke=\"#ef4444\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-base font-normal text-[var(--text-dark)]\" style=\"font-size:14px\">Budgets spiral out of control — surprises at every stage</span></li><li class=\"items-center\" style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:12px 0;min-height:48px;border-bottom:0.5px solid #e5e7eb\"><svg style=\"flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"9\" r=\"9\" fill=\"rgba(239,68,68,0.1)\"></circle><path d=\"M6 6l6 6M12 6l-6 6\" stroke=\"#ef4444\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-base font-normal text-[var(--text-dark)]\" style=\"font-size:14px\">Quality depends on labor &amp; site conditions — no consistency\t</span></li><li class=\"items-center\" style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:12px 0;min-height:48px;border-bottom:0.5px solid #e5e7eb\"><svg style=\"flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"9\" r=\"9\" fill=\"rgba(239,68,68,0.1)\"></circle><path d=\"M6 6l6 6M12 6l-6 6\" stroke=\"#ef4444\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-base font-normal text-[var(--text-dark)]\" style=\"font-size:14px\">Endless noise, dust &amp; disruption — impacts your business\t</span></li><li class=\"items-center\" style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:12px 0;min-height:48px;border-bottom:0.5px solid #e5e7eb\"><svg style=\"flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"9\" r=\"9\" fill=\"rgba(239,68,68,0.1)\"></circle><path d=\"M6 6l6 6M12 6l-6 6\" stroke=\"#ef4444\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-base font-normal text-[var(--text-dark)]\" style=\"font-size:14px\">Massive material wastage — inefficient and costly\t</span></li><li class=\"items-center\" style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:12px 0;min-height:48px;border-bottom:0.5px solid #e5e7eb\"><svg style=\"flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"9\" r=\"9\" fill=\"rgba(239,68,68,0.1)\"></circle><path d=\"M6 6l6 6M12 6l-6 6\" stroke=\"#ef4444\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-base font-normal text-[var(--text-dark)]\" style=\"font-size:14px\">Weather delays your progress — timelines keep slipping\t</span></li><li class=\"items-center\" style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:12px 0;min-height:48px;border-bottom:0.5px solid #e5e7eb\"><svg style=\"flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"9\" r=\"9\" fill=\"rgba(239,68,68,0.1)\"></circle><path d=\"M6 6l6 6M12 6l-6 6\" stroke=\"#ef4444\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-base font-normal text-[var(--text-dark)]\" style=\"font-size:14px\">Hard to expand or modify later — you’re locked in\t</span></li><li class=\"items-center\" style=\"display:flex;gap:10px;padding:12px 0;min-height:48px;border-bottom:none\"><svg style=\"flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"9\" r=\"9\" fill=\"rgba(239,68,68,0.1)\"></circle><path d=\"M6 6l6 6M12 6l-6 6\" stroke=\"#ef4444\" stro